{"tid":1836181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔好掛住武漢 留意返重要嘢 特朗普：第二階段經貿談判討論香港問題及中國人權","createTime":"2020-01-23T06:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T14:12:39.000Z","uid":34942,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"938a3385e516e156f900414ea61cf3ff029fcb95","tid":1836181,"uid":34942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1255012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1255012&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fpwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=a174b0b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1255012</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普指，中國人權記錄及香港問題是兩國第二階段經貿談判的內容一部份。在瑞士達沃斯出席世界經濟論壇的特朗普在記者會說，希望可以在中港問題上做一些事，又指雙方現正討論。但他沒有透露第二階段談判的時間表及限期。特朗普又提及中國在第一階段經貿協議承諾，未來兩年購買二千億美元的美國貨。他預料數額會隨著時間增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲唔快啲簽聯署？<br />\n聯署 要求美國將香港雙普選放入第二階段貿易協議<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fpwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=a0d66b7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人贏都唔想？<br />\n得六萬人簽咗？ Spread ！！！！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n廢除功能組別，2020雙普選</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"384d55c0fddf2b519e67cf05b1321e9966190ce6","tid":1836181,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:24:35.000Z","msg":"我簽左啦，你呢？"},{"pid":"1cab1945bcf4c34218557a212562f